hopobject.body: How many weeks' holiday a year are there? what to buy in spanish pharmacy In news out of Germany, Chancellor Angela Merkel said she has established initial contacts with Sigmar Gabriel, leader of the Opposition center-left Social Democratic Party, for talks on a coalition to rule the country for a consecutive third term. Merkel, meanwhile, stressed that she saw no need to change her policy on Greece and other debt-stricken Eurozone countries seeking financial bailouts.
